Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:13.59,0:52:20.50,ed_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,あなたが今も息をしている{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:21.27,0:52:30.28,ed_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,それだけでもう胸はいっぱい{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:30.90,0:52:38.61,ed_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,心の震えあらわす言葉は{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:38.74,0:52:46.72,ed_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,うまく探せないけど{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:47.28,0:52:54.06,ed_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,あなたのほほえみ きれいな旋律{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:54.14,0:53:03.51,ed_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,春の野原いちめんに開く小花{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:03.98,0:53:11.58,ed_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,やわらかな日ざし 恵の雨粒が{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:11.97,0:53:17.84,ed_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,降りそそぎますように{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:18.31,0:53:23.65,ed_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,天を見上げた{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:13.59,0:52:20.50,ed_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你如今仍在轻轻呼吸{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:21.27,0:52:30.28,ed_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,只要这样就能填满我心{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:30.90,0:52:38.61,ed_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,然而心中悸动{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:38.74,0:52:46.72,ed_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,却难以言表{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:47.28,0:52:54.06,ed_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你的微笑是那绮丽的旋律{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:54.14,0:53:03.51,ed_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,仿佛春天原野上遍开的小花{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:03.98,0:53:11.58,ed_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,温暖的阳光 恩惠的雨点{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:11.97,0:53:17.84,ed_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,祈祷着它们快些降临{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:18.31,0:53:23.65,ed_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,抬头望向天空{\fad(200,200)}
